)@@G@@URE PROCESS\TYPESETTER\OUTPUT   IMPORTED ('TSFDFUNC');@F@@@@PROCEDURE PRYH
)@@G@@OCESS\MERGENTHALER\OUTPUT IMPORTED ('M202FDFUNC');    @#@@@@CONTROL(EJECYI
)@@G@@T);   @[@@@@"     @[@@@@"     @B@@@@" THE FOLLOWING FUNCTIONS USED BY DPYJ
)@@G@@S     @F@@@@" ARE DEVICE DEPENDENT AND HENCE CALL UPON THE DEVICE HANDLEYK
)@@G@@R     @C@@@@" TO ACTUALLY PERFORM THE REQUESTED FUNCTION.   @[@@@@"     YL
)@@G@@@B@@@@PROCEDURE INITIALIZE EXPORTED ('INILZE')  @[@@@@BEGIN @B@@@@      YM
)@@G@@    FD\FUNCTION := FD\INITIALIZE;   @G@@@@          SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(YN
)@@G@@REAL\DEVICE\INDEX); " FIRST REAL DEVICE   @C@@@@          IF PROOFING THYO
)@@G@@EN " THEN IF PROOFING   @G@@@@             SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(PROOFER);YP
)@@G@@ " INITIALIZE PROOFER TOO     @#@@@@END; " INITIALIZE @[@@@@      @C@@@@YQ
)@@G@@PROCEDURE OUTPUT\LEADING(LED: WORD INTEGER)     @ @@@@           EXPORTEYR
)@@G@@D ('OUTLED')@[@@@@BEGIN @E@@@@          IF NOT INHIBIT\OUTPUT THEN      YS
)@@G@@" ALLOW OUTPUT    @#@@@@           BEGIN  @B@@@@             LEADING\FORYT
)@@G@@\DEVICE := LED;   @B@@@@             FD\FUNCTION := FD\LEADING;   @C@@@@YU
)@@G@@             SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVICE\INDEX); @#@@@@           END;   YV
)@@G@@@[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @C@@@@PROCEDURE PERFORM\PAGEUP EXPORTED ('PERPUPYW
)@@G@@')    @[@@@@BEGIN @E@@@@          IF NOT INHIBIT\OUTPUT THEN      " ALLOYX
)@@G@@W OUTPUT    @#@@@@           BEGIN  @B@@@@             FD\FUNCTION := FDYY
)@@G@@\PAGEUP;    @C@@@@             SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVICE\INDEX); @#@@@@YZ
)@@G@@           END;   @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @C@@@@PROCEDURE OUTPUT\TO\DEVIZA
)@@G@@CE EXPORTED ('OUTDEV')  @[@@@@BEGIN @E@@@@          IF NOT INHIBIT\OUTPUZB
)@@G@@T THEN      " ALLOW OUTPUT    @#@@@@           BEGIN  @B@@@@            ZC
)@@G@@ FD\FUNCTION := FD\OUTPUT;    @C@@@@             SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVZD
)@@G@@ICE\INDEX); @#@@@@           END;   @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @D@@@@PROCEDZE
)@@G@@URE PROCESS\START\OF\TAKE EXPORTED ('PROSOT')   @[@@@@BEGIN @A@@@@      ZF
)@@G@@    FD\FUNCTION := FD\SOT;    @C@@@@          SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVICEZG
)@@G@@\INDEX);    @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @D@@@@PROCEDURE PROCESS\END\OF\TAKE ZH
)@@G@@EXPORTED ('PROEOT')     @[@@@@BEGIN @E@@@@          IF NOT INHIBIT\OUTPUZI
)@@G@@T THEN      " ALLOW OUTPUT    @#@@@@           BEGIN  @A@@@@            ZJ
)@@G@@ FD\FUNCTION := FD\EOT; @C@@@@             SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVICE\INZK
)@@G@@DEX); @#@@@@           END;   @[@@@@END;  @E@@@@PROCEDURE OUTPUT\HARDWARZL
)@@G@@E\FONT\CHANGE EXPORTED ('FONTC')    @[@@@@BEGIN @B@@@@          FD\FUNCTZM
)@@G@@ION := FD\EXTERNAL\FONT;@C@@@@          SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVICE\INDEXZN
)@@G@@);    @#@@@@          END;    @[@@@@"     @F@@@@" WE WANT THE FONT DIRECZO
)@@G@@TIVE TO BE SCANNED BY THE ACTUAL FINAL    @F@@@@" DEVICE HANDLER, SO THEZP
)@@G@@ WIDTH TABLES WILL BE PROPERLY SET. THE   @E@@@@" GLOBAL VARIABLE REAL\DZQ
)@@G@@EVICE\INDEX HAS THE PROPER INDEX.   @[@@@@"     @E@@@@PROCEDURE PROCESS\ZR
)@@G@@INTERNAL\FONT\CHANGE EXPORTED ('CKFONT')  @[@@@@BEGIN @B@@@@          FDZS
)@@G@@\FUNCTION := FD\INTERNAL\FONT;@D@@@@          SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(REAL\DZT
)@@G@@EVICE\INDEX);     @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @G@@@@" SIMILARLY, WE WANT THEZU
)@@G@@ TYPESIZE DIRECTIVE TO BE SCANNED BY THE ACTUAL @H@@@@" FINAL DEVICE HANZV
)@@G@@DLER. THIS AND THE ABOVE ENSURES THAT THE LINE AND PAGE     @G@@@@" BREAZW
)@@G@@KS CORRESPOND BETWEEN PROOF AND FINAL FOR ANY GIVEN DOCUMENT.     @[@@@@ZX
)@@G@@"     @F@@@@PROCEDURE PROCESS\INTERNAL\TYPESIZE\CHANGE EXPORTED ('INTTYPZY
)@@G@@ECHG')@[@@@@BEGIN @C@@@@          FD\FUNCTION := FD\TYPESIZE\CHANGE;    ZZ
)@@G@@@D@@@@          SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(REAL\DEVICE\INDEX);     @[@@@@END;  AA
)@@G@@@[@@@@      @F@@@@PROCEDURE OUTPUT\HARDWARE\HEIGHT\CHANGE EXPORTED ('HEIAB
)@@G@@GHTCHANGE') @[@@@@BEGIN @D@@@@          FD\FUNCTION := FD\EXTERNAL\HEIGHAC
)@@G@@T\CHANGE;   @C@@@@          SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVICE\INDEX);    @[@@@@AD
)@@G@@END;  @[@@@@      @F@@@@PROCEDURE OUTPUT\HARDWARE\WIDTH\CHANGE EXPORTED AE
)@@G@@('WIDTHCHANGE')   @[@@@@BEGIN @D@@@@          FD\FUNCTION := FD\EXTERNALAF
)@@G@@\WIDTH\CHANGE;    @C@@@@          SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVICE\INDEX);    AG
)@@G@@@[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @C@@@@PROCEDURE PROCESS\DSI\BEGIN EXPORTED ('FDHAH
)@@G@@DSIB')@[@@@@BEGIN @E@@@@          IF NOT INHIBIT\OUTPUT THEN      " ALLOAI
)@@G@@W OUTPUT    @#@@@@           BEGIN  @A@@@@             FD\FUNCTION := FDAJ
)@@G@@\DSIB;@C@@@@             SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVICE\INDEX); @#@@@@      AK
)@@G@@     END;   @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @D@@@@PROCEDURE PROCESS\DSI\SWITCH EAL

)@@G@@ FD\FUNCTION := FD\DSIS;@C@@@@             SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVICE\INAO
)@@G@@DEX); @#@@@@           END;   @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @C@@@@PROCEDURE PRAP

)@@G@@CE(DEVICE\INDEX); @#@@@@           END;   @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @E@@@@AT

)@@G@@           BEGIN  @C@@@@             FD\FUNCTION := FD\END\OF\LINE;     AW
)@@G@@@C@@@@             SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVICE\INDEX); @#@@@@           EAX
)@@G@@ND;   @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @E@@@@PROCEDURE PROCESS\ESCAPE\SEQUENCE EXAY
)@@G@@PORTED ('DEVICESC')     @[@@@@BEGIN @C@@@@          FD\FUNCTION := FD\ESAZ
)@@G@@CAPE\SEQUENCE;    @C@@@@          SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVICE\INDEX);    BA
)@@G@@@[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @G@@@@PROCEDURE PROCESS\DEVICE\TRANSPARENT\OUTPUBB
)@@G@@T EXPORTED ('DEVICETRANS')    @[@@@@BEGIN @A@@@@          IF NOT INHIBITBC
)@@G@@\OUTPUT THEN@#@@@@           BEGIN  @D@@@@             FD\FUNCTION := FDBD
)@@G@@\TRANSPARENT\OUTPUT;    @C@@@@             SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(DEVICE\INBE
)@@G@@DEX); @#@@@@           END;   @B@@@@END; " OF PROCEDURE TRANSPARENT OUTPBF
)@@G@@UT    @[@@@@      @#@@@@CONTROL(EJECT);   @[@@@@"     @E@@@@" THE FD\FUNBG
)@@G@@CTION CODE HAS BEEN PLACED IN 'FD\FUNCTION' NOW @A@@@@" CALL THE ACTUAL BH
)@@G@@DEVICE HANDLER.   @[@@@@"     @I@@@@PROCEDURE SELECT\FINAL\DEVICE(INDEX:BI
)@@G@@ INTEGER WORD) " USUALLY DEVICE\INDEX BUT..     @[@@@@BEGIN @C@@@@      BJ
)@@G@@    CASEENTRY INDEX " SELECT FINAL DEVICE @[@@@@"     @^@@@@          CABK
)@@G@@SE PRINTER: @A@@@@             PROCESS\PRINTER\OUTPUT;@^@@@@          CABL
)@@G@@SE PHOTON:  @A@@@@             PROCESS\PHOTON\OUTPUT; @^@@@@          CABM
)@@G@@SE DURA:    @A@@@@             PROCESS\DURA\OUTPUT;   @^@@@@          CABN
)@@G@@SE QUALTERM:@B@@@@             PROCESS\QUALTERM\OUTPUT;     @ @@@@      BO
)@@G@@    CASE SPINTRONIC:    @B@@@@             PROCESS\SPINTRONIC\OUTPUT;   BP
)@@G@@@^@@@@          CASE PR770:   @A@@@@             PROCESS\PR770\OUTPUT;  BQ
)@@G@@@^@@@@          CASE TERMINAL:@B@@@@             PROCESS\TERMINAL\OUTPUTBR
)@@G@@;     @^@@@@          CASE LED120:  @A@@@@             PROCESS\LED120\OUBS
)@@G@@TPUT; @ @@@@          CASE FOTOTRONIC:    @B@@@@             PROCESS\FOTBT
)@@G@@OTRONIC\OUTPUT;   @^@@@@          CASE PROOFER: @A@@@@             PROCEBU
)@@G@@SS\PROOFER\OUTPUT;@ @@@@          CASE PRINTRONIX:    @B@@@@            BV
)@@G@@ PROCESS\PRINTRONIX\OUTPUT;   @ @@@@          CASE TYPESETTER:    @B@@@@BW
)@@G@@             PROCESS\TYPESETTER\OUTPUT;   @ @@@@          CASE MERGENTHABX
)@@G@@LER:  @B@@@@             PROCESS\MERGENTHALER\OUTPUT; @#@@@@          CABY

)@@G@@       [NEW\UDIR\BACK\LINK: 18 BIT INTEGER@C@@@@             ,NEW\UDIR\FKV

)@@G@@             ,NEW\UDIR\ENTRY(55):   @E@@@@                [NEW\UNIT\FLAGKX
)@@G@@S: 18 BIT UNSIGNED INTEGER    @E@@@@                ,NEW\UNIT\PAGE:  18 KY
)@@G@@BIT UNSIGNED INTEGER    @E@@@@                ,NEW\UNIT\CHAPTER: 18 BIT KZ
)@@G@@UNSIGNED INTEGER  @E@@@@                ,NEW\UNIT\SECTION: 18 BIT UNSIGNLA
)@@G@@ED INTEGER  @C@@@@                ,NEW\UNIT\ADDR: INTEGER WORD    @C@@@@LB
)@@G@@                ,NEW\UNIT\CKPT: INTEGER WORD    @#@@@@                ] LC
)@@G@@@#@@@@             ];   @[@@@@"     @A@@@@" LEVEL 5 OVERLAY OF FILE HEADLD
)@@G@@ER.   @[@@@@"     @E@@@@DEFINE    FILE\HEADER\LENGTH = 28; " WORD LENGTHLE
)@@G@@ OF HEADER  @F@@@@DECLARE   FILE\HEADER: MAPPED STATIC LOCATABLE IMPORTELF
)@@G@@D ('FILHDR')@[@@@@"     @ @@@@      "1" [*: WORD LOGICAL    @ @@@@      LG
)@@G@@"2" ,*: WORD LOGICAL    @C@@@@      "3" ,FILE\HEADER\LEVEL: 18 BIT INTEGLH
)@@G@@ER    @D@@@@          ,FILE\HEADER\BLOCK\WORD\SIZE: 18 BIT INTEGER@C@@@@LI
)@@G@@      "4" ,LINK\TO\UNIT\DIRECTORY: WORD INTEGER @C@@@@      "5" ,LINK\TOLJ
)@@G@@\FILE\BIT\MAP: WORD INTEGER   @C@@@@      "6" ,FILE\BIT\MAP\WORDS: WORD LK
)@@G@@INTEGER     @C@@@@      "7" ,LINK\TO\TOC: WORD INTEGER LOCATABLE  @B@@@@LL
)@@G@@      "8" ,LINK\TO\INDEX: WORD INTEGER    @B@@@@      "9" ,NUMBER\OF\UNILM
)@@G@@TS: WORD INTEGER  @B@@@@     "10" ,TRACKS\IN\FILE: WORD INTEGER   @A@@@@LN
)@@G@@     "11" ,MAXBITMAPS: WORD INTEGER @C@@@@     "12" ,LINK\TO\STATIC\HEADLO
)@@G@@ER: WORD INTEGER  @C@@@@     "13" ,HEADER\GLOBAL\CKPT: WORD INTEGER     LP
)@@G@@@F@@@@     "XX" ,*(15): INTEGER WORD]; " KEEP TOTAL LENGTH 28 WORDS     LQ
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @D@@@@" LEVEL 4 UNIT COMMON - TRANSLATED TO CHECKPOINT.     LR
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @D@@@@DECLARE   OLD\UNIT\COMMON: STATIC MAPPED LOCATABLE    LS
)@@G@@@A@@@@             [*(2): WORD INTEGER    @D@@@@             ,OLD\POINT\LT
)@@G@@SIZE: LOCATABLE INTEGER WORD  @C@@@@             ,OLD\FONT: LOCATABLE INLU
)@@G@@TEGER WORD  @A@@@@             ,*(2): INTEGER WORD    @D@@@@            LV
)@@G@@ ,OLD\TOP\MARGIN: LOCATABLE INTEGER WORD  @E@@@@             ,OLD\BOTTOMLW
)@@G@@\MARGIN: LOCATABLE INTEGER WORD     @A@@@@             ,*(4): WORD INTEGLX
)@@G@@ER    @D@@@@             ,OLD\PAGE\HEIGHT: LOCATABLE INTEGER WORD @D@@@@LY
)@@G@@             ,OLD\PAGE\WIDTH: LOCATABLE INTEGER WORD  @D@@@@            LZ
)@@G@@ ,OLD\LEADING: LOCATABLE INTEGER WORD     @E@@@@             ,*: INTEGERMA
)@@G@@ WORD " UNUSED WAS VERTICAL\POSITION@D@@@@             ,OLD\PAGE\NUMBER:MB
)@@G@@ LOCATABLE INTEGER WORD @E@@@@             ,OLD\CHAPTER\NUMBER(9): LOCATMC
)@@G@@ABLE INTEGER WORD @A@@@@             ,*(198): WORD INTEGER  @#@@@@      MD
)@@G@@       ];   @#@@@@CONTROL(EJECT);   @[@@@@"     @^@@@@" CONVERT FILE LEVME
)@@G@@ELS.  @[@@@@"     @D@@@@PROCEDURE CONVERT\LEVEL4\TO\LEVEL5 EXPORTED ('CVMF
)@@G@@TL45')@[@@@@BEGIN @C@@@@          WORD\COUNT(CUR\PKT) := BLOCKWORDS;    MG
)@@G@@@C@@@@          WORD\COUNT(NXT\PKT) := BLOCKWORDS;    @ @@@@          CVMH
)@@G@@T\UNIT\DIRECTORY; @D@@@@          TRACKS\IN\FILE := MAX\ALLOCATED\FILE\BMI
)@@G@@LOCK; @D@@@@          FILE\HEADER\LEVEL := 5; " SET FILE LEVEL    @C@@@@MJ
)@@G@@          WRITE\FILE\HEADER; " TO SCRATCH FILE  @C@@@@          SWITCH\FMK
)@@G@@ILES; " FOR NEXT CONVERSION   @A@@@@END; " CONVERT\LEVEL4\TO\LEVEL5     ML
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @A@@@@" CONVERSION UTILITY PROCEDURES.    @[@@@@"     @F@@@@MM
)@@G@@PROCEDURE CVT\READ\BLOCK(DRUM: INTEGER WORD " OLD DRUM ADDRESS    @E@@@@MN
)@@G@@                        ,RBUF: MACHINE POINTER) " TO BUFFER @[@@@@BEGIN MO
)@@G@@@D@@@@DECLARE   TEMP\SAVE: MACHINE POINTER; " TO BUFFER     @[@@@@"     MP
)@@G@@@E@@@@          TEMP\SAVE := BUFFER\ADDR(CUR\PKT); " SAVE BUFFER  @F@@@@MQ
)@@G@@          DRUM\ADDR(CUR\PKT) := CUR\BAS + DRUM; " SET READ ADDRESS@E@@@@MR
)@@G@@          BUFFER\ADDR(CUR\PKT) := RBUF; " SET READ BUFFER   @B@@@@      MS
)@@G@@    IOWWEC(CUR\PKT); " READ BLOCK IN@F@@@@          BUFFER\ADDR(CUR\PKT)MT
)@@G@@ := TEMP\SAVE; " RESTORE BUFFER     @^@@@@END; " CVT\READ\BLOCK   @[@@@@MU
)@@G@@"     @F@@@@PROCEDURE CVT\WRITE\BLOCK(DRUM: INTEGER WORD " NEW DRUM ADDRMV
)@@G@@ESS   @E@@@@                         ,WBUF: MACHINE POINTER) " TO BUFFERMW
)@@G@@@[@@@@BEGIN @D@@@@DECLARE   TEMP\SAVE: MACHINE POINTER; " TO BUFFER     MX
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @E@@@@          TEMP\SAVE := BUFFER\ADDR(NXT\PKT); " SAVE BUMY
)@@G@@FFER  @E@@@@          DRUM\ADDR(NXT\PKT) := DRUM; " SET DRUM ADDRESS    MZ
)@@G@@@E@@@@          BUFFER\ADDR(NXT\PKT) := WBUF; " SET BUFFER ADDRESS@C@@@@NA
)@@G@@          IOWWEC(NXT\PKT); " WRITE THE BLOCK OUT@F@@@@          BUFFER\ANB
)@@G@@DDR(NXT\PKT) := TEMP\SAVE; " RESTORE BUFFER     @^@@@@END; " CVT\WRITE\BNC
)@@G@@LOCK  @[@@@@"     @F@@@@" WRITE THE FILE HEADER BACK TO THE SCRATCH FILEND
)@@G@@ SO THAT RECOVERY @ @@@@" CAN GET THE CORRECT HEADER. @[@@@@"     @ @@@@NE
)@@G@@PROCEDURE WRITE\FILE\HEADER   @[@@@@BEGIN @D@@@@DECLARE   TEMP\SAVE: MACNF
)@@G@@HINE POINTER; " TO BUFFER     @[@@@@"     @E@@@@          TEMP\SAVE := BNG
)@@G@@UFFER\ADDR(NXT\PKT); " SAVE BUFFER  @D@@@@          DRUM\ADDR(NXT\PKT) :NH
)@@G@@= 0; " ADDRESS ZERO     @D@@@@          WORD\COUNT(NXT\PKT) := FILE\HEADNI
)@@G@@ER\LENGTH;  @D@@@@          BUFFER\ADDR(NXT\PKT) := LOC(FILE\HEADER);   NJ
)@@G@@@B@@@@          IOWWEC(NXT\PKT); " WRITE IT     @F@@@@          BUFFER\ANK
)@@G@@DDR(NXT\PKT) := TEMP\SAVE; " RESTORE BUFFER     @^@@@@END; " WRITE\FILE\NL
)@@G@@HEADER@#@@@@CONTROL(EJECT);   @[@@@@"     @D@@@@" CONVERT THE UNIT DIRECNM
)@@G@@TORY FROM LEVEL 4 TO LEVEL 5. @[@@@@"     @ @@@@PROCEDURE CVT\UNIT\DIRECNN
)@@G@@TORY  @[@@@@BEGIN @D@@@@DECLARE   OLD\INDEX: INTEGER WORD; " OLD UDIR INNO
)@@G@@DEX   @D@@@@DECLARE   NEW\INDEX: INTEGER WORD; " NEW UDIR INDEX   @H@@@@NP
)@@G@@DECLARE   NEW\UDIR\ADDR: INTEGER WORD; " ADDRESS FOR CURRENT OUTPUT BLOCNQ
)@@G@@K     @[@@@@"     @H@@@@" THE DRUM ADDRESS OF THE NEXT BLOCK TO READ IS NR
)@@G@@KEPT IN OLD\UDIR\FWRD\LINK    @G@@@@" THE DRUM ADDRESS OF THE CURRENT OUNS
)@@G@@TPUT BLOCK IS KEPT IN NEW\UDIR\ADDR @[@@@@"     @I@@@@          CVT\READNT
)@@G@@\BLOCK(LINK\TO\UNIT\DIRECTORY,LOC(OLD\UNIT\DIRECTORY)); " READ    @B@@@@NU
)@@G@@          OLD\INDEX := 0; " UNIT ZERO     @[@@@@"     @H@@@@          NENV
)@@G@@W\UDIR\ADDR := ALLOCATE\FILE\BLOCK(BLOCKWORDS); " SET UP WRITE    @G@@@@NW
)@@G@@          LINK\TO\UNIT\DIRECTORY := NEW\UDIR\ADDR; " SET UDIR START     NX
)@@G@@@B@@@@          NEW\INDEX := 0; " UNIT ZERO     @D@@@@          NEW\UDIRNY
)@@G@@\BACK\LINK := 0; " NO BACK LINK     @[@@@@"     @B@@@@" LOOP CONVERTING NZ
)@@G@@UNIT DIRECTORY ENTRIES. @[@@@@"     @C@@@@          FOR UNIT := 0 TO NUMOA
)@@G@@BER\OF\UNITS DO   @B@@@@           BEGIN " CONVERT UDIR ENTRY     @E@@@@OB
)@@G@@             OLD\INDEX := OLD\INDEX + 1; " INCREMENT INDEX  @F@@@@      OC
)@@G@@       IF (OLD\INDEX GT 111) THEN " MUST READ NEW BLOCK     @B@@@@      OD
)@@G@@        BEGIN " READ UDIR BLOCK     @H@@@@                CVT\READ\BLOCKOE
)@@G@@(OLD\UDIR\FWRD\LINK,LOC(OLD\UNIT\DIRECTORY));   @C@@@@                OLOF
)@@G@@D\INDEX := 1; " RESET INDEX   @A@@@@              END; " READ UDIR BLOCKOG
)@@G@@@E@@@@             NEW\INDEX := NEW\INDEX + 1; " INCREMENT INDEX  @F@@@@OH
)@@G@@             IF (NEW\INDEX GT 55) THEN " MUST WRITE NEW BLOCK     @B@@@@OI
)@@G@@              BEGIN " WRITE UDIR BLOCK    @G@@@@                NEW\UDIROJ
)@@G@@\FWRD\LINK := ALLOCATE\FILE\BLOCK(BLOCKWORDS);  @G@@@@                CVOK
)@@G@@T\WRITE\BLOCK(NEW\UDIR\ADDR,LOC(NEW\UNIT\DIRECTORY)); @D@@@@            OL
)@@G@@    NEW\UDIR\BACK\LINK := NEW\UDIR\ADDR; "@D@@@@                NEW\UDIROM
)@@G@@\ADDR := NEW\UDIR\FWRD\LINK;  @D@@@@                NEW\INDEX := 1; " SEON
)@@G@@T INDEX TO ONE    @B@@@@              END; " WRITE UDIR BLOCK     @[@@@@OO
)@@G@@"     @A@@@@" COPY UNIT ENTRY MOVING THINGS.    @[@@@@"     @G@@@@      OP
)@@G@@       NEW\UNIT\FLAGS(NEW\INDEX) := OLD\UNIT\FLAGS(OLD\INDEX);    @F@@@@OQ
)@@G@@             NEW\UNIT\PAGE(NEW\INDEX) := OLD\UNIT\PAGE(OLD\INDEX);@E@@@@OR
)@@G@@             NEW\UNIT\CHAPTER(NEW\INDEX) := 0; " NO CHAPTER @E@@@@      OS
)@@G@@       NEW\UNIT\SECTION(NEW\INDEX) := 0; " NO SECTION @E@@@@            OT
)@@G@@ CVT\UNIT\TEXT(OLD\INDEX,NEW\INDEX); " COPY TEXT@A@@@@           END; " OU
)@@G@@CONVERT\UDIR\ENTRY@D@@@@          NEW\UDIR\FWRD\LINK := 0; " SET FWRD ZEOV
)@@G@@RO    @F@@@@          CVT\WRITE\BLOCK(NEW\UDIR\ADDR,LOC(NEW\UNIT\DIRECTOOW
)@@G@@RY)); @ @@@@END; " CVT\UNIT\DIRECTORY     @#@@@@CONTROL(EJECT);   @[@@@@OX
)@@G@@"     @F@@@@" THIS PROCEDURE IS CALLED FROM CVT\UNIT\DIRECTORY TO COPY TOY
)@@G@@HE    @A@@@@" TEXT WHILE CONVERTING ITS FORMAT. @[@@@@"     @G@@@@PROCEDOZ
)@@G@@URE CVT\UNIT\TEXT(OLD\INDEX: INTEGER WORD  " INDEX IN OLD UDIR    @G@@@@PA
)@@G@@                       ,NEW\INDEX: INTEGER WORD) " INDEX IN NEW UDIR    PB
)@@G@@@[@@@@BEGIN @D@@@@          NEW\UNIT\ADDR(NEW\INDEX) := 0; " INITIALIZE PC
)@@G@@@D@@@@          NEW\UNIT\CKPT(NEW\INDEX) := 0; " INITIALIZE @C@@@@      PD
)@@G@@    IF OLD\UNIT\ADDR(OLD\INDEX) NE 0 THEN @A@@@@           BEGIN " COPY PE
)@@G@@THE UNIT    @G@@@@             DRUM\ADDR(CUR\PKT) := OLD\UNIT\ADDR(OLD\IPF
)@@G@@NDEX)+CUR\BAS;    @C@@@@             IOWWEC(CUR\PKT); " READ FIRST BLOCKPG
)@@G@@@E@@@@             IF HEADER\LINK(BUFFER\ADDR(CUR\PKT)) NE 0 THEN @C@@@@PH
)@@G@@                NEW\UNIT\CKPT(NEW\INDEX) :=     @G@@@@                  PI
)@@G@@ CVT\UNIT\HEADER(HEADER\LINK(BUFFER\ADDR(CUR\PKT)));  @G@@@@            PJ
)@@G@@ DRUM\ADDR(CUR\PKT) := NEXT\BLOCK(BUFFER\ADDR(CUR\PKT));    @[@@@@"     PK
)@@G@@@G@@@@             DRUM\ADDR(NXT\PKT) := ALLOCATE\FILE\BLOCK(BLOCKWORDS)PL
)@@G@@;     @G@@@@             NEW\UNIT\ADDR(NEW\INDEX) := DRUM\ADDR(NXT\PKT);PM
)@@G@@ " SET START@G@@@@             BUFFER\ADDR(NXT\PKT) :=: BUFFER\ADDR(CUR\PN
)@@G@@PKT); " SWITCH    @E@@@@             PREVIOUS\BLOCK(BUFFER\ADDR(NXT\PKT)PO
)@@G@@) := 0;     @[@@@@"     @D@@@@             WHILE ( DRUM\ADDR(CUR\PKT) NEPP
)@@G@@ 0 ) DO     @B@@@@              BEGIN " COPY ANOTHER BLOCK  @F@@@@      PQ
)@@G@@          DRUM\ADDR(CUR\PKT) := DRUM\ADDR(CUR\PKT)+CUR\BAS; @D@@@@      PR
)@@G@@          IO(CUR\PKT); " READ NEXT BLOCK ASYNCH @D@@@@                NEPS
)@@G@@XT\BLOCK(BUFFER\ADDR(NXT\PKT)) :=   @D@@@@                   ALLOCATE\FIPT
)@@G@@LE\BLOCK(BLOCKWORDS);   @C@@@@                IOWWEC(NXT\PKT); " WRITE BPU
)@@G@@UFFER @C@@@@                WAITEC(CUR\PKT); " WAIT FOR READ@G@@@@      PV
)@@G@@          DRUM\ADDR(CUR\PKT) := NEXT\BLOCK(BUFFER\ADDR(CUR\PKT)); @G@@@@PW
)@@G@@                BUFFER\ADDR(CUR\PKT) :=: BUFFER\ADDR(NXT\PKT); " SWITCH PX
)@@G@@@E@@@@                PREVIOUS\BLOCK(BUFFER\ADDR(NXT\PKT)) :=     @B@@@@PY
)@@G@@                    DRUM\ADDR(NXT\PKT);   @G@@@@                DRUM\ADDPZ
)@@G@@R(NXT\PKT) := NEXT\BLOCK(BUFFER\ADDR(CUR\PKT)); @B@@@@              END;QA
)@@G@@ " COPY ANOTHER BLOCK   @F@@@@             NEXT\BLOCK(BUFFER\ADDR(NXT\PKQB
)@@G@@T)) := 0; " TERMINATE   @C@@@@             IOWWEC(NXT\PKT); " WRITE LASTQC
)@@G@@ BLOCK@A@@@@           END; " COPY THE UNIT     @^@@@@END; " CVT\UNIT\TEQD
)@@G@@XT    @#@@@@CONTROL(EJECT);   @C@@@@PROCEDURE CVT\UNIT\HEADER(ADDR: INTEQE
)@@G@@GER WORD)   @F@@@@          RESULT INTEGER WORD " ADDRESS OF CHECKPOINT QF
)@@G@@PRODUCED    @[@@@@BEGIN @E@@@@DECLARE   UNIT\CKPT: INTEGER WORD; " DRUM QG
)@@G@@ADDRESS OF CKPT   @[@@@@"     @F@@@@          CVT\READ\BLOCK(ADDR,LOC(OLQH
)@@G@@D\UNIT\COMMON)); " READ IT    @D@@@@"         SNAP('OLDCOM',26,LOC(OLD\UQI
)@@G@@NIT\COMMON));     @A@@@@          UNIT\CKPT := 0; " CLEAR IT@E@@@@      QJ
)@@G@@    CKPT\IMAGE\PTR := ALLOCATE\CORE(1+MAX\DATA\IMAGE);@E@@@@          CKQK
)@@G@@PT\PKT := NULL\PTR; " SO FILE WILL INITIALIZE   @F@@@@          INITIALIQL
)@@G@@ZE\FILE( %CKPT\PKT , %CKPT\IMAGE\PTR , 0 );     @[@@@@"     @C@@@@" WRITQM
)@@G@@E CHECKPOINT OF UNIT COMMON VARIABLES.    @[@@@@"     @[@@@@"     @G@@@@QN
)@@G@@" DATA ITEMS WHICH WERE REPRESENTED IN THE LEVEL 4 UNIT HEADERS ARE     QO
)@@G@@@F@@@@" WRITTEN INTO THE LEVEL 5 CHECKPOINT FILE.  OTHER DATA ITEMS ARE QP
)@@G@@@G@@@@" OUTPUT FROM THE DBANK.  IT IS ASSUMED THAT INTERN-INIT HAS SET TQQ
)@@G@@HESE  @D@@@@" TO SOME REASONABLE VALUE. (*=FROM OLD UNIT HEADER). @[@@@@QR
)@@G@@"     @A@@@@" WRITE SINGLE INTEGER VARIABLES    @[@@@@"     @E@@@@      QS
)@@G@@    WRITE\UHDR\INT(CTYP\PAGE,OLD\PAGE\NUMBER); " *    @D@@@@          WRQT
)@@G@@ITE\UHDR\INT(CTYP\FONT,OLD\FONT); " *     @F@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\INTQU
)@@G@@(CTYP\HEADL,HEADING\LENGTH); " NO HEADING @F@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\INTQV
)@@G@@(CTYP\FOOTL,FOOTING\LENGTH); " NO FOOTING @D@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\INTQW
)@@G@@(CTYP\CHTHI,CHARS\THIS\LINE); @D@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\INT(CTYP\CHNXT,QX
)@@G@@CHARS\NEXT\LINE); @[@@@@"     @A@@@@" WRITE SINGLE DISTANCE VARIABLES   QY
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @E@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\PTSIZE,OLD\POINT\SIZE); QZ
)@@G@@" *   @E@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\PAGWID,OLD\PAGE\WIDTH); " *   RA
)@@G@@@E@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\PAGHIT,OLD\PAGE\HEIGHT); " *  @D@@@@RB
)@@G@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\LEAD,OLD\LEADING); " *  @D@@@@          WRRC
)@@G@@ITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\SPREM,SPACE\REMAINING); @E@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DSTRD
)@@G@@(CTYP\VPOSN,VERTICAL\POSITION);     @[@@@@"     @ @@@@" WRITE CONDITION RE
)@@G@@VARIABLES.  @[@@@@"     @C@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\LFLAG,LEFT\FRF
)@@G@@LAG); @E@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\NUMBOT,NUMBER\BOTTOM\OF\PAGE);RG
)@@G@@@E@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\EDCHAP,EDIT\CHAP\NUMBER);     @E@@@@RH
)@@G@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\STPAGE,START\PAGE\NUMBERING); @D@@@@      RI
)@@G@@    WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\ODDPAG,ODD\PAGE\FACING);@D@@@@          WRITE\UHRJ
)@@G@@DR\CND(CTYP\HEADC,CENTER\HEADING);  @D@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\RK
)@@G@@FOOTC,CENTER\FOOTING);  @E@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\HEADR,HEADINRL
)@@G@@G\REQUESTED);     @E@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\FOOTR,FOOTING\REQURM
)@@G@@ESTED);     @[@@@@"     @ @@@@" WRITE MULTI-WORD VARIABLES. @[@@@@"     RN
)@@G@@@G@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CKPT(CTYP\CHAP,9,LOC(OLD\CHAPTER\NUMBER(1)));RO
)@@G@@ " *  @G@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CKPT(CTYP\HEADT,MAX\HDG\WORDS,LOC(HEADIRP
)@@G@@NG\CORE));  @G@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CKPT(CTYP\FOOTT,MAX\HDG\WORDS,LOCRQ
)@@G@@(FOOTING\CORE));  @[@@@@"     @H@@@@" SEE CORRESPONDING COMMENT IN ELEMERR
)@@G@@NT CHECKPOINT-ROUTINE WRITE\UNIT\CKPT.    @[@@@@"     @C@@@@          IFRS
)@@G@@ (AREA\TYPE NE TEXT) THEN ERROR;    @F@@@@          IF (BUFFER\TEXT OR IRT
)@@G@@NHIBIT\DISTRIBUTION) THEN ERROR;    @[@@@@"     @C@@@@" WRITE CHECKPOINTRU
)@@G@@ OF AREA\BASED UNIT ITEMS.    @[@@@@"     @A@@@@" WRITE SINGLE INTEGER VRV
)@@G@@ARIABLES.   @[@@@@"     @D@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\INT(CTYP\COLNM,COLUMNRW
)@@G@@\NUMBER);   @E@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\INT(CTYP\COLNT,NUMBER\OF\COLUMNS)RX
)@@G@@;     @[@@@@"     @A@@@@" WRITE SINGLE DISTANCE VARIABLES.  @[@@@@"     RY
)@@G@@@D@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\GUTRW,GUTTER\WIDTH);    @D@@@@      RZ
)@@G@@    WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\LINDE,LEFT\INDENT);     @D@@@@          WRITE\UHSA
)@@G@@DR\DST(CTYP\RINDE,RIGHT\INDENT);    @C@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\SB
)@@G@@AVPOS,AREA\VPOS); @D@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\AREAHT,AREA\HEIGHTSC
)@@G@@);    @D@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\AREAWD,AREA\WIDTH);     @D@@@@SD
)@@G@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\ARVPOS,AREA\REL\VPOS);  @D@@@@          WRSE
)@@G@@ITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\AVPOSS,AREA\VPOS\START);@D@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DSTSF
)@@G@@(CTYP\LFTOFF,LEFT\OFFSET);    @E@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\TOPMARSG
)@@G@@,OLD\TOP\MARGIN); " *   @E@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\BOTMAR,OLD\BSH
)@@G@@OTTOM\MARGIN); " *@D@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\LFTMAR,LEFT\MARGINSI
)@@G@@);    @D@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\DST(CTYP\RGTMAR,RIGHT\MARGIN);   @[@@@@SJ
)@@G@@"     @A@@@@" WRITE SINGLE CONDITION VARIABLES. @[@@@@"     @C@@@@      SK
)@@G@@    WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\BALFL,BALANCING); @C@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CNDSL
)@@G@@(CTYP\CENFL,CENTER);    @C@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\COMFL,COMPACSM
)@@G@@T);   @D@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\DISFL,DISTRIBUTION);    @B@@@@SN
)@@G@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\FILFL,FILL);@C@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CNDSO
)@@G@@(CTYP\HYPFL,HYPHEN);    @C@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\JUSFL,JUSTIFSP
)@@G@@Y);   @E@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\JUSTRT,JUSTIFY\FROM\RIGHT);   SQ
)@@G@@@C@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\NOSFL,NOSPACE);   @C@@@@          WRSR
)@@G@@ITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\RITEF,RIGHTF);    @D@@@@          WRITE\UHDR\CND(CTYP\SS
)@@G@@UNDOT,AREA\UNDERLINE);  @[@@@@"     @C@@@@          CLOSE\FILE(CKPT\PKT)ST
)@@G@@; " CLOSE FILE    @F@@@@          UNIT\CKPT := START\DRUM\ADDR(CKPT\PKT)SU
)@@G@@; " GET ADDRESS   @D@@@@          RELEASE\CORE(CKPT\PKT); " RELEASE PACKSV
)@@G@@ET    @B@@@@          RETURN(UNIT\CKPT); " TO CALLER  @^@@@@END; " CVT\USW
)@@G@@NIT\HEADER  @#@@@@CONTROL(EJECT);   @[@@@@"     @[@@@@"     @B@@@@" WRITSX
)@@G@@E ONE INTEGER WORD FROM ARGUMENT.   @[@@@@"     @^@@@@PROCEDURE WRITE\UHSY
)@@G@@DR\INT@E@@@@             (CKPT\ID: INTEGER WORD " ID FOR CHECKPOINT     SZ
)@@G@@@D@@@@             ,DATA\WORD: INTEGER WORD " DATA TO WRITE @#@@@@      TA
)@@G@@       )    @[@@@@BEGIN @E@@@@          CKPT\DATA\INT(1) := DATA\WORD; "TB
)@@G@@ SET DATA WORD    @D@@@@          WRITE\CKPT\IMAGE(CKPT\ID,1); " ONE WORTC
)@@G@@D     @B@@@@"         ODISPLAY('WUHINT',DATA\WORD);   @^@@@@END; " WRITETD
)@@G@@\UHDR\INT   @[@@@@"     @[@@@@"     @B@@@@" WRITE ONE DISTANCE WORD FROMTE
)@@G@@ ARGUMENT.  @[@@@@"     @^@@@@PROCEDURE WRITE\UHDR\DST@E@@@@            TF
)@@G@@ (CKPT\ID: INTEGER WORD " ID FOR CHECKPOINT     @D@@@@             ,DATATG
)@@G@@\WORD: DISTANCE " DATA TO WRITE     @#@@@@             )    @[@@@@BEGIN TH
)@@G@@@E@@@@          CKPT\DATA\DST(1) := DATA\WORD; " SET DATA WORD    @D@@@@TI
)@@G@@          WRITE\CKPT\IMAGE(CKPT\ID,1); " ONE WORD     @B@@@@"         ODTJ
)@@G@@ISPLAY('WUHDST',DATA\WORD);   @^@@@@END; " WRITE\UHDR\DST   @[@@@@"     TK
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @B@@@@" WRITE ONE CONDITION WORD FROM ARGUMENT. @[@@@@"     TL
)@@G@@@^@@@@PROCEDURE WRITE\UHDR\CND@E@@@@             (CKPT\ID: INTEGER WORD TM
)@@G@@" ID FOR CHECKPOINT     @E@@@@             ,DATA\WORD: WORD CONDITION " TN
)@@G@@DATA TO WRITE     @#@@@@             )    @[@@@@BEGIN @E@@@@          CKTO
)@@G@@PT\DATA\CND(1) := DATA\WORD; " SET DATA WORD    @D@@@@          WRITE\CKTP
)@@G@@PT\IMAGE(CKPT\ID,1); " ONE WORD     @B@@@@"         ODISPLAY('WUHCND',DATQ
)@@G@@TA\WORD);   @^@@@@END; " WRITE\UHDR\CND   @[@@@@"     @[@@@@"     @F@@@@TR
)@@G@@" WRITE CONSTANT AMOUNT OF DATA FROM DBANK.  NOTE THAT IT MUST    @^@@@@TS
)@@G@@" FIT IN ONE DATA IMAGE.@[@@@@"     @E@@@@PROCEDURE WRITE\UHDR\CKPT(CKPTTT
)@@G@@\ID: INTEGER WORD " IMAGE TYPE@F@@@@                         ,DATA\LEN: TU
)@@G@@INTEGER WORD " LENGTH IN WORDS@F@@@@                         ,DATA\ADR: TV
)@@G@@MACHINE POINTER) " ADDRESS    @[@@@@BEGIN @C@@@@DECLARE   DATA(1): INTEGTW
)@@G@@ER WORD BASED(DATA\ADR);@[@@@@"     @A@@@@          FOR I := 1 TO DATA\LTX
)@@G@@EN DO @F@@@@             CKPT\DATA\INT(I) := DATA(I); " COPY DATA TO IMATY
)@@G@@GE    @C@@@@          WRITE\CKPT\IMAGE(CKPT\ID,DATA\LEN);   @^@@@@END; "TZ
)@@G@@ WRITE\UHDR\CKPT  @[@@@@"     @[@@@@"     @E@@@@" THIS PROCEDURE IS CALLUA
)@@G@@ED TO WRITE THE CHECKPOINT IMAGE    @ @@@@" INTO THE CHECKPOINT FILE.   UB
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @ @@@@PROCEDURE WRITE\CKPT\IMAGE    @F@@@@             (CKPTUC
)@@G@@\ID: INTEGER WORD " TYPE OF CHECKPOINT IMAGE    @F@@@@             ,DATAUD
)@@G@@\LEN: INTEGER WORD) " LENGTH OF DATA (IN WORDS) @[@@@@BEGIN @A@@@@      UE
)@@G@@    CKPT\TYPE := CKPT\ID;     @C@@@@          CKPT\SPARE := 0; " CLEAR SUF
)@@G@@PARE FIELD  @F@@@@          IF (DATA\LEN GT MAX\DATA\IMAGE) THEN ERROR; UG
)@@G@@" $$$DEBUG  @ @@@@          INCLUDE(WRITE\SNAP);@D@@@@             SNAP(UH
)@@G@@'CKPTWR',DATA\LEN+1,CKPT\IMAGE\PTR);@#@@@@          RESUME; @D@@@@      UI
)@@G@@    WRITE\FILE(CKPT\PKT , 4*(DATA\LEN+1) );     @ @@@@END; " OF WRITE\CKUJ
)@@G@@PT\IMAGE    @[@@@@TERM; ___@@@;     @ @@@@END; " OF WRITE\CKPT\IMAGE    UK
)@@G@@*[S@@@*SDFF*@[@@@@MODULE@A@@@@          COPY ('DEFINES',IMPORTED);@A@@@@UL
)@@G@@ COPY ('DEBUG-PROCS',IMPORTED);     @B@@@@          COPY ('CARD-DEF',IMPUM
)@@G@@ORTED);     @B@@@@          COPY ('CHAR-SIZE',IMPORTED);    @B@@@@      UN
)@@G@@    COPY ('GETPUT-DEF',IMPORTED);   @B@@@@          COPY ('AREA-DEF',IMPUO
)@@G@@ORTED);     @B@@@@          COPY ('SCAN-PROCS',IMPORTED);   @B@@@@      UP
)@@G@@    COPY ('STAGING-DEF',IMPORTED);  @B@@@@          COPY ('SYMBOL-DEF',IUQ
)@@G@@MPORTED);   @B@@@@          COPY ('TITLE-DEF',IMPORTED);    @B@@@@      UR
)@@G@@    COPY ('UNIT-COMMON',IMPORTED);  @B@@@@          COPY ('WARNING-DEF',US
)@@G@@IMPORTED);  @[@@@@      @F@@@@PROCEDURE PACK\CHARACTER(CHAR: WORD INTEGEUT
)@@G@@R) IMPORTED ('PAKCHR'); @[@@@@      @F@@@@PROCEDURE GET\TRANSPARENT\CHARUU
)@@G@@ACTER IMPORTED ('GETTRANSCHAR')     @A@@@@             RESULT WORD INTEGUV

)@@G@@');   @[@@@@      @D@@@@PROCEDURE PR\PAGEUP\TERMINAL IMPORTED ('PAGUPT')UX
)@@G@@;     @[@@@@      @C@@@@PROCEDURE PR\PAGEUP\FILE IMPORTED ('PAGUPF');   UY
)@@G@@@[@@@@      @E@@@@PROCEDURE SET\ALL\AREA\LINE\WIDTHS IMPORTED ('SETALLINUZ
)@@G@@WID');@[@@@@      @F@@@@DECLARE   LEADING\FOR\DEVICE: DISTANCE STATIC IMVA
)@@G@@PORTED ('LEDDEV');@[@@@@      @C@@@@DECLARE   SKIP: WORD INTEGER STATIC VB
)@@G@@IMPORTED;   @[@@@@      @H@@@@DECLARE   XXXX: WORD INTEGER; " GETS RID OVC
)@@G@@F COLLECTOR ERRORS WHEN NO DBANK    @[@@@@"     @C@@@@PROCEDURE INITIALIVD
)@@G@@ZE\PRINTER EXPORTED ('PRINIT')@[@@@@BEGIN @A@@@@          UNIT\DEVICE\WIVE
)@@G@@DTH := 1; " @E@@@@          NEW\CHAR\WIDTH := 10; " TEN CHARACTERS PER IVF
)@@G@@NCH   @B@@@@          CHANGE\CHARS\PER\INCH; " SET IT @[@@@@"     @^@@@@VG
)@@G@@" SET STANDARD MARGINS  @[@@@@"     @B@@@@          TOP\MARGIN := INCH\DVH
)@@G@@ISTANCE;    @B@@@@          BOTTOM\MARGIN := INCH\DISTANCE; @C@@@@      VI
)@@G@@    PAGE\HEIGHT := INCH\DISTANCE * 11;    @C@@@@          PAGE\WIDTH := VJ
)@@G@@INCH\DISTANCE * 8.5;    @B@@@@          LEFT\MARGIN := INCH\DISTANCE;   VK
)@@G@@@B@@@@          RIGHT\MARGIN := INCH\DISTANCE;  @A@@@@          SET\ALL\VL
)@@G@@AREA\LINE\WIDTHS; @F@@@@          NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT := 8; " SET 8 LINES PEVM
)@@G@@R INCH STANDARD   @B@@@@          CHANGE\LINES\PER\INCH; " SET IT @F@@@@VN
)@@G@@          PAGE\OFFSET := INCH\DISTANCE * 2.4; " OFFSET 2.4 INCHES @E@@@@VO
)@@G@@          DEVICE\BACKSPACES := FALSE; " WE CAN'T BACKSPACE  @F@@@@      VP
)@@G@@    DEVICE\LETTER\SPACES := FALSE; " CANNOT LETTERSPACE     @D@@@@      VQ
)@@G@@    DEVICE\JUSTIFIES := FALSE; " WE MUST DO IT  @F@@@@          DEVICE\HVR
)@@G@@YPHEN\CHAR := MINUS; " STANDARD HYPHEN CHAR     @E@@@@          MUTILATEVS
)@@G@@ := TRUE; " FORMAT OVERSTRIKES FOR PRINTER@[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @C@@@@VT
)@@G@@PROCEDURE PAGEUP\PRINTER EXPORTED ('PRTOPFRM')  @[@@@@BEGIN @C@@@@      VU
)@@G@@    IF OUTPUT\MEDIA EQ MEDIA\HERE THEN    @A@@@@             PR\PAGEUP\TVV
)@@G@@ERMINAL;    @D@@@@          ELSE IF OUTPUT\MEDIA EQ MEDIA\FILE THEN     VW
)@@G@@@#@@@@           BEGIN  @ @@@@             PR\PAGEUP\FILE;  @D@@@@      VX
)@@G@@       SKIP := -1; " COMPENSATE FOR PRINTER     @#@@@@           END;   VY
)@@G@@@[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @B@@@@" DO ACTUAL LINE FEEDS FOR THE PRINTER    VZ
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @D@@@@PROCEDURE LINE\FEED\PRINTER EXPORTED ('PRLEADNG')     WA
)@@G@@@[@@@@BEGIN @F@@@@          SKIP := SKIP + LEADING\FOR\DEVICE // SKIP\DIWB
)@@G@@STANCE;     @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @A@@@@PROCEDURE CHANGE\LINES\PER\INCWC
)@@G@@H     @[@@@@BEGIN @E@@@@          SKIP\DISTANCE := INTERNAL // NEW\CHAR\WD
)@@G@@HEIGHT;     @G@@@@          LINES\PER\INCH := NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT; " SET FORWE
)@@G@@ OUTPUT HANDLER   @[@@@@"     @B@@@@" SET STANDARD LEADING FOR LINE PRINWF
)@@G@@TER   @[@@@@"     @A@@@@          LEADING := SKIP\DISTANCE; @C@@@@      WG
)@@G@@    TYPESIZE\HEIGHT := SKIP\DISTANCE;     @B@@@@          UNIT\LEADING :WH
)@@G@@= SKIP\DISTANCE;  @B@@@@          SECTION\LEADING\BEFORE(1) := 0; @E@@@@WI
)@@G@@          SECTION\LEADING\AFTER(1) := SKIP\DISTANCE * 3;    @E@@@@      WJ
)@@G@@    SECTION\LEADING\BEFORE(2) := SKIP\DISTANCE * 2;   @D@@@@          SEWK
)@@G@@CTION\LEADING\AFTER(2) := SKIP\DISTANCE;  @D@@@@          SECTION\LEADINWL
)@@G@@G\BEFORE(3) := SKIP\DISTANCE; @D@@@@          SECTION\LEADING\AFTER(3) :WM
)@@G@@= SKIP\DISTANCE;  @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @A@@@@PROCEDURE CHANGE\CHARS\PWN
)@@G@@ER\INCH     @[@@@@BEGIN @D@@@@          IU\DU\FACTOR := INTERNAL // NEW\WO
)@@G@@CHAR\WIDTH; @F@@@@          UNIT\INTERNAL\WIDTH := IU\DU\FACTOR*UNIT\DEVWP
)@@G@@ICE\WIDTH;  @B@@@@          COLUMN\DISTANCE := IU\DU\FACTOR;@C@@@@      WQ
)@@G@@    SPACEBAND\WIDTH := COLUMN\DISTANCE;   @C@@@@          TYPESIZE\WIDTHWR
)@@G@@ := COLUMN\DISTANCE;    @[@@@@"     @ @@@@" INITIALIZE CHARACTER SIZES  WS
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @ @@@@          FOR I := 1 TO 256 DO@C@@@@             CHAR\WT
)@@G@@WIDTH(I) := SPACEBAND\WIDTH;  @H@@@@          CHAR\WIDTH(BACKSPACE+1) :=WU
)@@G@@ - SPACEBAND\WIDTH; " BACKSPACE WIDTH     @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @C@@@@WV
)@@G@@" PACK THE CHARACTERS JUST GIVEN INTO THE LINE  @F@@@@" THE LINE IS NOT WW
)@@G@@ACTUALLY OUTPUT UNTIL THE END\OF\LINE SUBROUTINE@]@@@@" IS CALLED @[@@@@WX
)@@G@@"     @D@@@@PROCEDURE PACK\PRINTER\LINE EXPORTED ('PROUTPUT')     @[@@@@WY
)@@G@@ BEGIN@[@@@@"     @B@@@@" PACK FROM LINE\BUFFER TO OUTPUT\CARD    @[@@@@WZ
)@@G@@"     @A@@@@          IF TRANSPARENT\OUTPUT THEN@C@@@@             FOR IXA
)@@G@@ := LINE\START TO LINE\END DO @C@@@@                PACK\CHARACTER(LINE\XB
)@@G@@BUFFER(I)); @#@@@@          ELSE    @#@@@@           BEGIN  @C@@@@      XC
)@@G@@       FOR I := LINE\START TO LINE\END DO @^@@@@              BEGIN     XD
)@@G@@@F@@@@                IF LINE\BUFFER(I) EQ BLANK OR " HANDLE BLANKS     XE
)@@G@@@G@@@@                   LINE\BUFFER(I) EQ FUNC\SPACEBAND THEN " HANDLE XF
)@@G@@BLANKS@^@@@@                 BEGIN  @G@@@@                   FOR K := 1 XG
)@@G@@TO LINE\CHAR\WIDTH(I)//SPACEBAND\WIDTH DO @C@@@@                      PAXH
)@@G@@CK\CHARACTER(BLANK);    @^@@@@                 END;   @C@@@@            XI
)@@G@@    ELSE " ALL OTHER CHARACTERS     @D@@@@                   PACK\CHARACXJ
)@@G@@TER(LINE\BUFFER(I));    @#@@@@              END;@#@@@@           END;   XK
)@@G@@@[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @D@@@@" CLOSE THE LINE AND OUTPUT IT TO THE FINAXL
)@@G@@L MEDIUM    @[@@@@"     @E@@@@" DUMP THE LINE OUT  BUT FIRST BLANK FILL XM
)@@G@@THE LAST WORD     @[@@@@"     @D@@@@PROCEDURE OUTPUT\PRINTER\LINE EXPORTXN
)@@G@@ED ('PRENDLIN')   @[@@@@BEGIN @A@@@@          OUTPUT\LINE; " DUMP LINE  XO
)@@G@@@[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @E@@@@" HERE WE MAKE INTERNAL ADJUSTMENTS DUE TOXP
)@@G@@ A TYPESIZE CHANGE@D@@@@" ASSUMING OF COURSE THAT THE CHANGE IS LEGITIMAXQ
)@@G@@TE.   @[@@@@"     @E@@@@PROCEDURE PRINTER\TYPESIZE\CHANGE EXPORTED ('PRIXR
)@@G@@NSIZE')     @[@@@@BEGIN @ @@@@DECLARE TLEN: WORD INTEGER;   @ @@@@DECLARXS
)@@G@@E TNUM(2): WORD INTEGER;@ @@@@          NEW\CHAR\WIDTH := 0;@A@@@@      XT
)@@G@@    NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT := 0;     @D@@@@          SCAN(CTRM+ALLOW\DST+COMA+AXU
)@@G@@LLOW\INT+EVAL);   @H@@@@          TLEN := CSDLEN;    " SAVE THESE VALUESXV
)@@G@@ AND THEN CALL SCANNER AGAIN  @ @@@@          TNUM(1) := DNUM(1); @ @@@@XW
)@@G@@          TNUM(2) := DNUM(2); @F@@@@          SCAN(CTRM+ALLOW\INT+EVAL);XX
)@@G@@ " THIS TIME PICK THEM ALL UP @^@@@@          CASEENTRY TLEN@#@@@@      XY
)@@G@@    CASE 0: @A@@@@             IF CSDLEN EQ 1 THEN    @C@@@@            XZ
)@@G@@    NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT := DNUM(1);     @#@@@@          CASE 1: @#@@@@      YA
)@@G@@     BEGIN  @B@@@@             NEW\CHAR\WIDTH := TNUM(1);   @A@@@@      YB
)@@G@@       IF CSDLEN EQ 1 THEN    @C@@@@                NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT := DYC
)@@G@@NUM(1);     @A@@@@             IF CSDLEN GT 1 THEN    @A@@@@            YD
)@@G@@    NEW\CHAR\WIDTH := 0;@#@@@@           END;   @#@@@@          CASE 2: YE
)@@G@@@A@@@@             IF CSDLEN EQ 0 THEN    @^@@@@              BEGIN     YF
)@@G@@@B@@@@                NEW\CHAR\WIDTH := TNUM(1);@C@@@@                NEYG
)@@G@@W\CHAR\HEIGHT := TNUM(2);     @#@@@@              END;@#@@@@          ENYH
)@@G@@DCASE;@E@@@@          IF (NEW\CHAR\WIDTH NE 0 OR NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT NE 0)  YI
)@@G@@@C@@@@             AND ERROR\STATUS\CODE EQ 0 THEN    @#@@@@           BYJ
)@@G@@EGIN  @E@@@@             IF (NEW\CHAR\WIDTH EQ 0 OR NEW\CHAR\WIDTH EQ 10YK
)@@G@@@G@@@@                  OR NEW\CHAR\WIDTH EQ 12) AND (NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT EQYL
)@@G@@ 0    @G@@@@                  OR NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT EQ 6 OR NEW\CHAR\HEIGHTYM
)@@G@@ EQ 8) THEN @^@@@@              BEGIN     @C@@@@                IF NEW\CYN
)@@G@@HAR\WIDTH NE 0 THEN     @B@@@@                   CHANGE\CHARS\PER\INCH; YO
)@@G@@@C@@@@                IF NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT NE 0 THEN    @B@@@@            YP
)@@G@@       CHANGE\LINES\PER\INCH; @#@@@@              END;@#@@@@           EYQ
)@@G@@ND;   @#@@@@          ELSE    @A@@@@             WARNING(W\DIR\SYNTAX); YR
)@@G@@@[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @B@@@@" PROCEDURE TO HANDLE TRANSPARENT OUTPUT  YS
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @D@@@@PROCEDURE PR\TRANSPARENT\OUTPUT EXPORTED ('PRTNSDAT') YT
)@@G@@@[@@@@BEGIN @[@@@@      @ @@@@DECLARE   CHAR: WORD INTEGER; @[@@@@      YU
)@@G@@@B@@@@          WHILE TRANSPARENT\OUTPUT DO     @#@@@@           BEGIN  YV
)@@G@@@C@@@@             CHAR := GET\TRANSPARENT\CHARACTER; @D@@@@            YW
)@@G@@ IF TRANSPARENT\OUTPUT THEN " STUFF IT    @D@@@@                PACK\CHAYX
)@@G@@RACTER(CHAR); " SEND IT OFF   @ @@@@           END; " WHILE LOOP  @B@@@@YY
)@@G@@END; " OF PROCEDURE TRANSPARENT OUTPUT    @[@@@@"     @D@@@@" UNUSED ENTYZ
)@@G@@RY POINTS FOR GENERALIZED PRINTER HANDLER.@[@@@@"     @G@@@@PROCEDURE PRZA
)@@G@@\START\OF\TAKE              EXPORTED ('PRSTRTAK') BEGIN END;@G@@@@PROCEDZB

)@@G@@R         EXPORTED ('PRESCAPE') BEGIN END;@[@@@@"     @[@@@@TERM; ___@@@ZL

)@@G@@    COLUMN\DISTANCE := IU\DU\FACTOR;@C@@@@          SPACEBAND\WIDTH := CZN

)@@G@@SPARENT\CHARACTER IMPORTED ('GETTRANSCHAR')     @A@@@@             RESULZW

)@@G@@INTEGER) IMPORTED ('PAKCHR'); @[@@@@      @B@@@@PROCEDURE OUTPUT\LINE IMZY

)@@G@@AGE   @[@@@@"     @H@@@@DECLARE   XXXX: WORD INTEGER; " GETS RID OF COLLAF
)@@G@@ECTOR ERRORS WHEN NO DBANK    @[@@@@      @D@@@@PROCEDURE INITIALIZE\TERAG
)@@G@@MINAL EXPORTED ('TERMLINIT')  @[@@@@BEGIN @A@@@@          UNIT\DEVICE\WIAH
)@@G@@DTH := 1; " @E@@@@          NEW\CHAR\WIDTH := 10; " TEN CHARACTERS PER IAI
)@@G@@NCH   @B@@@@          CHANGE\CHARS\PER\INCH; " SET IT @[@@@@"     @^@@@@AJ

)@@G@@    PAGE\HEIGHT := INCH\DISTANCE * 11;    @C@@@@          PAGE\WIDTH := AM

)@@G@@INE\WIDTHS; @F@@@@          NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT := 6; " SET 6 LINES PER INCHAP
)@@G@@ STANDARD   @B@@@@          CHANGE\LINES\PER\INCH; " SET IT @F@@@@      AQ
)@@G@@    PAGE\OFFSET := 0; " VIRTUAL AND PHYSICAL PAGE THE SAME  @E@@@@      AR
)@@G@@    DEVICE\BACKSPACES := TRUE; " WE CAN BACKSPACE     @F@@@@          DEAS
)@@G@@VICE\LETTER\SPACES := FALSE; " CANNOT LETTERSPACE     @D@@@@          DEAT
)@@G@@VICE\JUSTIFIES := FALSE; " WE MUST DO IT  @F@@@@          DEVICE\HYPHEN\AU
)@@G@@CHAR := MINUS; " STANDARD HYPHEN CHAR     @C@@@@          MUTILATE := FAAV
)@@G@@LSE; " DO NOT MUTILATE  @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @D@@@@PROCEDURE PAGEUP\TAW
)@@G@@ERMINAL EXPORTED ('TERMLTOPFRM')    @[@@@@BEGIN @C@@@@          IF OUTPUAX
)@@G@@T\MEDIA EQ MEDIA\HERE THEN    @#@@@@           BEGIN  @D@@@@            AY
)@@G@@ SKIP := SKIP + (PAGE\HEIGHT-PAGEUP\POS)  @E@@@@                // SKIP\AZ
)@@G@@DISTANCE; " SKIP TO BOTTOM OF PAGE  @A@@@@             OUTPUT\LINE; " DOBA

)@@G@@DIA\FILE THEN     @#@@@@           BEGIN  @ @@@@             PR\PAGEUP\FBC
)@@G@@ILE;  @D@@@@             SKIP := -1; " COMPENSATE FOR PRINTER     @#@@@@BD
)@@G@@           END;   @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @B@@@@" DO ACTUAL LINE FEEDS FBE
)@@G@@OR THE TERMINAL   @[@@@@"     @D@@@@PROCEDURE LINE\FEED\TERMINAL EXPORTEBF
)@@G@@D ('TERMLLEADNG') @[@@@@BEGIN @F@@@@          SKIP := SKIP + LEADING\FORBG
)@@G@@\DEVICE // SKIP\DISTANCE;     @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @F@@@@" HERE WE REBH
)@@G@@AD IN THE PARAMETERS FROM THE DIRECTIVE CALL AND IF   @C@@@@" VALID MAKEBI
)@@G@@ THE NECESSARY INTERNAL ADJUSTMENTS.@[@@@@"     @E@@@@PROCEDURE TERMINALBJ
)@@G@@\TYPESIZE\CHANGE EXPORTED ('TERMLINSIZE') @[@@@@BEGIN @A@@@@          COBK
)@@G@@PY ('TYPESIZE-MAC');    @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @A@@@@PROCEDURE CHANGE\LBL
)@@G@@INES\PER\INCH     @[@@@@BEGIN @E@@@@          SKIP\DISTANCE := INTERNAL BM
)@@G@@// NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT;     @G@@@@          LINES\PER\INCH := NEW\CHAR\HEIGHBN
)@@G@@T; " SET FOR OUTPUT HANDLER   @[@@@@"     @A@@@@" SET STANDARD LEADING FBO
)@@G@@OR TERMINAL @[@@@@"     @A@@@@          LEADING := SKIP\DISTANCE; @C@@@@BP
)@@G@@          TYPESIZE\HEIGHT := SKIP\DISTANCE;     @B@@@@          UNIT\LEABQ
)@@G@@DING := SKIP\DISTANCE;  @[@@@@"     @^@@@@" DEFINE SECTION LEADING@[@@@@BR
)@@G@@"     @B@@@@          SECTION\LEADING\BEFORE(1) := 0; @E@@@@          SEBS
)@@G@@CTION\LEADING\AFTER(1) := SKIP\DISTANCE * 3;    @E@@@@          SECTION\BT
)@@G@@LEADING\BEFORE(2) := SKIP\DISTANCE * 2;   @D@@@@          SECTION\LEADINBU
)@@G@@G\AFTER(2) := SKIP\DISTANCE;  @D@@@@          SECTION\LEADING\BEFORE(3) BV
)@@G@@:= SKIP\DISTANCE; @D@@@@          SECTION\LEADING\AFTER(3) := SKIP\DISTABW
)@@G@@NCE;  @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @A@@@@PROCEDURE CHANGE\CHARS\PER\INCH     BX
)@@G@@@[@@@@BEGIN @D@@@@          IU\DU\FACTOR := INTERNAL // NEW\CHAR\WIDTH; BY
)@@G@@@F@@@@          UNIT\INTERNAL\WIDTH := IU\DU\FACTOR*UNIT\DEVICE\WIDTH;  BZ
)@@G@@@B@@@@          COLUMN\DISTANCE := IU\DU\FACTOR;@C@@@@          SPACEBANCA
)@@G@@D\WIDTH := COLUMN\DISTANCE;   @C@@@@          TYPESIZE\WIDTH := COLUMN\DCB
)@@G@@ISTANCE;    @[@@@@"     @ @@@@" INITIALIZE CHARACTER SIZES  @[@@@@"     CC
)@@G@@@ @@@@          FOR I := 1 TO 256 DO@C@@@@             CHAR\WIDTH(I) := CD
)@@G@@SPACEBAND\WIDTH;  @H@@@@          CHAR\WIDTH(BACKSPACE+1) := - SPACEBANDCE
)@@G@@\WIDTH; " BACKSPACE WIDTH     @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @C@@@@" PACK THE CCF
)@@G@@HARACTERS JUST GIVEN INTO THE LINE  @F@@@@" THE LINE IS NOT ACTUALLY OUTCG
)@@G@@PUT UNTIL THE END\OF\LINE SUBROUTINE@]@@@@" IS CALLED @[@@@@"     @D@@@@CH
)@@G@@PROCEDURE PACK\TERMINAL\LINE EXPORTED ('TERMLOUTPUT') @[@@@@ BEGIN@[@@@@CI
)@@G@@"     @B@@@@" PACK FROM LINE\BUFFER TO OUTPUT\CARD    @[@@@@"     @A@@@@CJ
)@@G@@          IF TRANSPARENT\OUTPUT THEN@C@@@@             FOR I := LINE\STACK
)@@G@@RT TO LINE\END DO @C@@@@                PACK\CHARACTER(LINE\BUFFER(I)); CL
)@@G@@@#@@@@          ELSE    @#@@@@           BEGIN  @C@@@@             FOR ICM
)@@G@@ := LINE\START TO LINE\END DO @^@@@@              BEGIN     @F@@@@      CN
)@@G@@          IF LINE\BUFFER(I) EQ BLANK THEN " HANDLE BLANKS   @^@@@@      CO
)@@G@@           BEGIN  @G@@@@                   FOR K := 1 TO LINE\CHAR\WIDTHCP
)@@G@@(I)//SPACEBAND\WIDTH DO @C@@@@                      PACK\CHARACTER(BLANKCQ
)@@G@@);    @^@@@@                 END;   @C@@@@                ELSE " ALL OTHCR
)@@G@@ER CHARACTERS     @D@@@@                   PACK\CHARACTER(LINE\BUFFER(I)CS
)@@G@@);    @#@@@@              END;@#@@@@           END;   @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@CT
)@@G@@"     @D@@@@" CLOSE THE LINE AND OUTPUT IT TO THE FINAL MEDIUM    @[@@@@CU
)@@G@@"     @E@@@@" DUMP THE LINE OUT  BUT FIRST BLANK FILL THE LAST WORD     CV
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @E@@@@PROCEDURE OUTPUT\TERMINAL\LINE EXPORTED ('TERMLENDLIN'CW
)@@G@@)     @[@@@@BEGIN @A@@@@          OUTPUT\LINE; " DUMP LINE  @[@@@@END;  CX
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @B@@@@" PROCEDURE TO HANDLE TRANSPARENT OUTPUT  @[@@@@"     CY
)@@G@@@E@@@@PROCEDURE HANDLE\TRANSPARENT\OUTPUT EXPORTED ('TERMLTNSDAT')@[@@@@CZ
)@@G@@BEGIN @[@@@@      @ @@@@DECLARE   CHAR: WORD INTEGER; @[@@@@      @B@@@@DA
)@@G@@          WHILE TRANSPARENT\OUTPUT DO     @#@@@@           BEGIN  @C@@@@DB
)@@G@@             CHAR := GET\TRANSPARENT\CHARACTER; @D@@@@             IF TRDC
)@@G@@ANSPARENT\OUTPUT THEN " STUFF IT    @D@@@@                PACK\CHARACTERDD
)@@G@@(CHAR); " SEND IT OFF   @ @@@@           END; " WHILE LOOP  @B@@@@END; "DE
)@@G@@ OF PROCEDURE TRANSPARENT OUTPUT    @[@@@@"     @E@@@@" UNUSED ENTRY POIDF
)@@G@@NTS FOR GENERALIZED TERMINAL HANDLER.     @[@@@@"     @H@@@@PROCEDURE TEDG
)@@G@@RMINAL\START\OF\TAKE        EXPORTED ('TERMLSTRTAK') BEGIN END;   @H@@@@DH
)@@G@@PROCEDURE TERMINAL\END\OF\TAKE          EXPORTED ('TERMLENDTAK') BEGIN EDI
)@@G@@ND;   @H@@@@PROCEDURE TERMINAL\INTERNAL\FONT\CHANGE EXPORTED ('TERMLINFODJ
)@@G@@NT') BEGIN END;   @H@@@@PROCEDURE TERMINAL\EXTERNAL\FONT\CHANGE EXPORTEDDK
)@@G@@ ('TERMLEXFONT') BEGIN END;   @H@@@@PROCEDURE TERMINAL\EXTERNAL\HEIGHT  DL
)@@G@@    EXPORTED ('TERMLEXHGHT') BEGIN END;   @H@@@@PROCEDURE TERMINAL\EXTERDM
)@@G@@NAL\WIDTH       EXPORTED ('TERMLEXWIDT') BEGIN END;   @H@@@@PROCEDURE TEDN
)@@G@@RMINAL\SUPERIOR\BEGIN       EXPORTED ('TERMLDSIB')   BEGIN END;   @H@@@@DO
)@@G@@PROCEDURE TERMINAL\SUPERIOR\SWITCH      EXPORTED ('TERMLDSIS')   BEGIN EDP
)@@G@@ND;   @H@@@@PROCEDURE TERMINAL\SUPERIOR\END         EXPORTED ('TERMLDSIEDQ
)@@G@@')   BEGIN END;   @H@@@@PROCEDURE TERMINAL\ESCAPE\FOR\HANDLER   EXPORTEDDR
)@@G@@ ('TERMLESCAPE') BEGIN END;   @[@@@@"     @[@@@@TERM; ___@@@T MUTILATE  DS
)@@G@@@[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @D@@@@PROCEDURE PAGEUP\T*[S@@@*SDFF*@[@@@@MODULEDT
)@@G@@@A@@@@          COPY ('DEFINES',IMPORTED);@B@@@@          COPY('DEBUG-PRDU
)@@G@@OCS',IMPORTED);   @B@@@@          COPY ('CARD-DEF',IMPORTED);     @B@@@@DV
)@@G@@          COPY ('CHAR-SIZE',IMPORTED);    @B@@@@          COPY ('GETPUT-DW
)@@G@@DEF',IMPORTED);   @B@@@@          COPY ('GETPUT-PROCS',IMPORTED); @B@@@@DX
)@@G@@          COPY ('AREA-DEF',IMPORTED);     @B@@@@          COPY ('SCAN-PRDY
)@@G@@OCS',IMPORTED);   @B@@@@          COPY ('STAGING-DEF',IMPORTED);  @B@@@@DZ
)@@G@@          COPY ('SYMBOL-DEF',IMPORTED);   @B@@@@          COPY ('TITLE-DEA
)@@G@@EF',IMPORTED);    @B@@@@          COPY ('UNIT-COMMON',IMPORTED);  @B@@@@EB
)@@G@@          COPY ('WARNING-DEF',IMPORTED);  @[@@@@      @F@@@@PROCEDURE PAEC
)@@G@@CK\CHARACTER(CHAR: WORD INTEGER) IMPORTED ('PAKCHR'); @[@@@@      @B@@@@ED
)@@G@@PROCEDURE OUTPUT\LINE IMPORTED ('OPL');   @[@@@@      @E@@@@PROCEDURE SEEE
)@@G@@T\ALL\AREA\LINE\WIDTHS IMPORTED ('SETALLINWID');@[@@@@      @F@@@@PROCEDEF
)@@G@@URE GET\TRANSPARENT\CHARACTER IMPORTED ('GETTRANSCHAR')     @A@@@@      EG
)@@G@@       RESULT WORD INTEGER;   @[@@@@      @G@@@@DECLARE   LEADING\FOR\DEEH
)@@G@@VICE: WORD INTEGER STATIC IMPORTED ('LEDDEV');  @[@@@@      @C@@@@DECLAREI
)@@G@@E   SKIP: WORD INTEGER STATIC IMPORTED;   @[@@@@      @[@@@@"     @#@@@@EJ
)@@G@@" LOCAL STORAGE   @[@@@@"     @G@@@@DECLARE   HORIZONTAL: WORD INTEGER SEK
)@@G@@TATIC := 0; " NEEDED FOR SPEED TABS @D@@@@DECLARE   SPEED\TAB\POS: WORD EL
)@@G@@INTEGER STATIC := 0;    @B@@@@DECLARE   TAB\COLUMN: WORD INTEGER STATIC;EM
)@@G@@@C@@@@DECLARE   SPACE\OUT: WORD INTEGER STATIC := 0; "@[@@@@      @ @@@@EN
)@@G@@DEFINE    ESCAPE = O'33';     @A@@@@DEFINE    SET\SPEED\TAB = O'157';   EO
)@@G@@@ @@@@DEFINE    SPEED\TAB = O'71';  @[@@@@      @D@@@@PROCEDURE INITIALIEP
)@@G@@ZE\SPINTRONIC EXPORTED ('SPININIT') @[@@@@BEGIN @A@@@@          UNIT\DEVEQ
)@@G@@ICE\WIDTH := 1; " @E@@@@          NEW\CHAR\WIDTH := 10; " TEN CHARACTERSER
)@@G@@ PER INCH   @B@@@@          CHANGE\CHARS\PER\INCH; " SET IT @[@@@@"     ES
)@@G@@@^@@@@" SET STANDARD MARGINS  @[@@@@"     @B@@@@          TOP\MARGIN := ET
)@@G@@INCH\DISTANCE;    @B@@@@          BOTTOM\MARGIN := INCH\DISTANCE; @C@@@@EU
)@@G@@          PAGE\HEIGHT := INCH\DISTANCE * 11;    @C@@@@          PAGE\WIDEV
)@@G@@TH := INCH\DISTANCE * 8.5;    @B@@@@          LEFT\MARGIN := INCH\DISTANEW
)@@G@@CE;   @B@@@@          RIGHT\MARGIN := INCH\DISTANCE;  @A@@@@          SEEX
)@@G@@T\ALL\AREA\LINE\WIDTHS; @F@@@@          NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT := 6; " SET 6 LIEY
)@@G@@NES PER INCH STANDARD   @B@@@@          CHANGE\LINES\PER\INCH; " SET IT EZ
)@@G@@@F@@@@          PAGE\OFFSET := 0; " VIRTUAL AND PHYSICAL PAGE THE SAME  FA
)@@G@@@E@@@@          DEVICE\BACKSPACES := TRUE; " WE CAN BACKSPACE     @F@@@@FB
)@@G@@          DEVICE\LETTER\SPACES := FALSE; " CANNOT LETTERSPACE     @D@@@@FC
)@@G@@          DEVICE\JUSTIFIES := FALSE; " WE MUST DO IT  @F@@@@          DEFD
)@@G@@VICE\HYPHEN\CHAR := MINUS; " STANDARD HYPHEN CHAR     @C@@@@          MUFE
)@@G@@TILATE := FALSE; " DO NOT MUTILATE  @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @D@@@@PROCEDFF
)@@G@@URE PAGEUP\SPINTRONIC EXPORTED ('SPINTOPFRM')   @[@@@@BEGIN @C@@@@      FG
)@@G@@    SKIP := 0; " KILL PENDING SKIP COUNT  @E@@@@          PACK\CHARACTERFH
)@@G@@(FORM\FEED); " OUTPUT FORM FEED     @C@@@@          OUTPUT\SPINTRONIC\LIFI
)@@G@@NE; " DUMP IT     @F@@@@          SPEED\TAB\POS := 0; " RESET ALL SPEED FJ
)@@G@@TABS ON NEW PAGE  @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @B@@@@" DO ACTUAL LINE FEEDS FFK
)@@G@@OR THE SPINTRONIC @[@@@@"     @D@@@@PROCEDURE LINE\FEED\SPINTRONIC EXPORFL
)@@G@@TED ('SPINLEADNG')@[@@@@BEGIN @A@@@@          OUTPUT\LINE; " DUMP LINE  FM
)@@G@@@F@@@@          SKIP := SKIP + LEADING\FOR\DEVICE // SKIP\DISTANCE;     FN
)@@G@@@[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @F@@@@" HERE WE READ IN THE NUMBERS OFF THE DIREFO
)@@G@@CTIVE PARAMETERS, CHECK @E@@@@" THAT THEY ARE VALID AND PERFORM THE REQUFP
)@@G@@IRED FUNCTIONS    @[@@@@"     @E@@@@PROCEDURE SPINTRONIC\TYPESIZE\CHANGEFQ
)@@G@@ EXPORTED ('SPININSIZE')@[@@@@BEGIN @ @@@@DECLARE TLEN: WORD INTEGER;   FR
)@@G@@@ @@@@DECLARE TNUM(2): WORD INTEGER;@ @@@@          NEW\CHAR\WIDTH := 0;FS
)@@G@@@A@@@@          NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT := 0;     @B@@@@          SCAN(CTRM+COMAFT
)@@G@@+ALLOW\INT+EVAL); @H@@@@          TLEN := CSDLEN;    " SAVE THESE VALUESFU
)@@G@@ AND THEN CALL SCANNER AGAIN  @ @@@@          TNUM(1) := DNUM(1); @ @@@@FV
)@@G@@          TNUM(2) := DNUM(2); @F@@@@          SCAN(CTRM+ALLOW\INT+EVAL);FW
)@@G@@ " THIS TIME PICK THEM ALL UP @^@@@@          CASEENTRY TLEN@#@@@@      FX
)@@G@@    CASE 0: @A@@@@             IF CSDLEN EQ 1 THEN    @C@@@@            FY
)@@G@@    NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT := DNUM(1);     @#@@@@          CASE 1: @#@@@@      FZ
)@@G@@     BEGIN  @B@@@@             NEW\CHAR\WIDTH := TNUM(1);   @A@@@@      GA
)@@G@@       IF CSDLEN EQ 1 THEN    @C@@@@                NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT := DGB
)@@G@@NUM(1);     @A@@@@             IF CSDLEN GT 1 THEN    @A@@@@            GC
)@@G@@    NEW\CHAR\WIDTH := 0;@#@@@@           END;   @#@@@@          CASE 2: GD
)@@G@@@A@@@@             IF CSDLEN EQ 0 THEN    @^@@@@              BEGIN     GE
)@@G@@@B@@@@                NEW\CHAR\WIDTH := TNUM(1);@C@@@@                NEGF
)@@G@@W\CHAR\HEIGHT := TNUM(2);     @#@@@@              END;@#@@@@          ENGG
)@@G@@DCASE;@E@@@@          IF ERROR\STATUS\CODE EQ 0 AND (NEW\CHAR\WIDTH NE 0GH
)@@G@@@C@@@@                 OR NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT NE 0) THEN  @#@@@@           BGI
)@@G@@EGIN  @E@@@@             IF (NEW\CHAR\WIDTH EQ 0 OR NEW\CHAR\WIDTH EQ 10GJ
)@@G@@@F@@@@                OR NEW\CHAR\WIDTH EQ 12) AND (NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT EQ 0GK
)@@G@@@G@@@@                OR NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT EQ 6 OR NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT EQ 8) TGL
)@@G@@HEN   @^@@@@              BEGIN     @C@@@@                IF NEW\CHAR\WIGM
)@@G@@DTH NE 0 THEN     @B@@@@                   CHANGE\CHARS\PER\INCH; @C@@@@GN
)@@G@@                IF NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT NE 0 THEN    @^@@@@                 BGO
)@@G@@EGIN  @B@@@@                   CHECK\FOR\HEIGHT\FUNC; @B@@@@            GP
)@@G@@       CHANGE\LINES\PER\INCH; @^@@@@                 END;   @#@@@@      GQ
)@@G@@        END;@#@@@@             ELSE @B@@@@                WARNING(W\ILLEGR
)@@G@@GAL\POINT); @#@@@@           END;   @#@@@@          ELSE    @A@@@@      GS
)@@G@@       WARNING(W\DIR\SYNTAX); @[@@@@"     @[@@@@END;  @F@@@@" HERE WE CHGT
)@@G@@ECK THE CURRENT HEIGHT AND IF IT IS DIFFERENT THEN    @E@@@@" THE HEIGHTGU
)@@G@@ REQUESTED, WE PUT THE FUNCTION INTO THE WORD.  @[@@@@"     @A@@@@PROCEDGV
)@@G@@URE CHECK\FOR\HEIGHT\FUNC     @[@@@@BEGIN @D@@@@          IF NEW\CHAR\HEGW
)@@G@@IGHT NE LINES\PER\INCH THEN   @F@@@@             PUT\FUNCTION\INTO\WORD(GX
)@@G@@FUNC\HEIGHT,NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT); @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @F@@@@" HERE WE ACGY
)@@G@@TUALLY PUT IN THE REQUIRED SEQUENCE OF CHARACTERS TO  @B@@@@" MAKE THE SGZ
)@@G@@PINTRONIC CHANGE IT'S HEIGHT  @[@@@@"     @F@@@@PROCEDURE OUTPUT\HARDWARHA
)@@G@@E\HEIGHT\CHANGE EXPORTED ('SPINEXHGHT')   @[@@@@BEGIN @[@@@@"     @E@@@@HB
)@@G@@" THE REQUIRED SEQUENCE IS: ESC-7 (ASCII CHARS OF COURSE)   @[@@@@"     HC
)@@G@@@E@@@@" KEEP TURNED OFF FOR NOW BECAUSE ESC-7 CAUSES TOGGLE AND   @E@@@@HD
)@@G@@" WE CAN NOT BE SURE WHAT MODE WE ARE IN HENCE CURRENT CODE @C@@@@" CAN HE
)@@G@@ACTUALLY PUT US INTO WRONG LINES PER INCH.@[@@@@"     @A@@@@          INHF
)@@G@@CLUDE(FALSE); " TURN OFF@C@@@@          PACK\CHARACTER(O'33');  " ASCII HG
)@@G@@ESC   @B@@@@          PACK\CHARACTER(O'67'); " ASCII 7@B@@@@          REHH
)@@G@@SUME; " END OF TURNED OFF CODE@[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @A@@@@PROCEDURE CHHI
)@@G@@ANGE\LINES\PER\INCH     @[@@@@BEGIN @E@@@@          SKIP\DISTANCE := INTHJ
)@@G@@ERNAL // NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT;     @G@@@@          LINES\PER\INCH := NEW\CHARHK
)@@G@@\HEIGHT; " SET FOR OUTPUT HANDLER   @[@@@@"     @B@@@@" SET STANDARD LEAHL
)@@G@@DING FOR SPINTRONIC     @[@@@@"     @A@@@@          LEADING := SKIP\DISTHM
)@@G@@ANCE; @C@@@@          TYPESIZE\HEIGHT := SKIP\DISTANCE;     @B@@@@      HN
)@@G@@    UNIT\LEADING := SKIP\DISTANCE;  @[@@@@"     @^@@@@" DEFINE SECTION LHO
)@@G@@EADING@[@@@@"     @B@@@@          SECTION\LEADING\BEFORE(1) := 0; @E@@@@HP
)@@G@@          SECTION\LEADING\AFTER(1) := SKIP\DISTANCE * 3;    @E@@@@      HQ
)@@G@@    SECTION\LEADING\BEFORE(2) := SKIP\DISTANCE * 2;   @D@@@@          SEHR
)@@G@@CTION\LEADING\AFTER(2) := SKIP\DISTANCE;  @D@@@@          SECTION\LEADINHS
)@@G@@G\BEFORE(3) := SKIP\DISTANCE; @D@@@@          SECTION\LEADING\AFTER(3) :HT
)@@G@@= SKIP\DISTANCE;  @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @A@@@@PROCEDURE CHANGE\CHARS\PHU
)@@G@@ER\INCH     @[@@@@BEGIN @D@@@@          IU\DU\FACTOR := INTERNAL // NEW\HV
)@@G@@CHAR\WIDTH; @F@@@@          UNIT\INTERNAL\WIDTH := IU\DU\FACTOR*UNIT\DEVHW
)@@G@@ICE\WIDTH;  @B@@@@          COLUMN\DISTANCE := IU\DU\FACTOR;@C@@@@      HX
)@@G@@    SPACEBAND\WIDTH := COLUMN\DISTANCE;   @C@@@@          TYPESIZE\WIDTHHY
)@@G@@ := COLUMN\DISTANCE;    @[@@@@"     @ @@@@" INITIALIZE CHARACTER SIZES  HZ
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @ @@@@          FOR I := 1 TO 256 DO@C@@@@             CHAR\IA
)@@G@@WIDTH(I) := SPACEBAND\WIDTH;  @H@@@@          CHAR\WIDTH(BACKSPACE+1) :=IB
)@@G@@ - SPACEBAND\WIDTH; " BACKSPACE WIDTH     @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @C@@@@IC
)@@G@@" PACK THE CHARACTERS JUST GIVEN INTO THE LINE  @F@@@@" THE LINE IS NOT ID
)@@G@@ACTUALLY OUTPUT UNTIL THE END\OF\LINE SUBROUTINE@]@@@@" IS CALLED @[@@@@IE
)@@G@@"     @D@@@@PROCEDURE PACK\SPINTRONIC\LINE EXPORTED ('SPINOUTPUT')@[@@@@IF
)@@G@@ BEGIN@[@@@@"     @B@@@@" PACK FROM LINE\BUFFER TO OUTPUT\CARD    @[@@@@IG
)@@G@@"     @C@@@@          FOR I := LINE\START TO LINE\END DO    @#@@@@      IH
)@@G@@     BEGIN  @E@@@@             IF LINE\BUFFER(I) EQ BLANK THEN " HANDLE II
)@@G@@BLANKS@^@@@@              BEGIN     @E@@@@                SPACE\OUT := SIJ
)@@G@@PACE\OUT + LINE\CHAR\WIDTH(I);@#@@@@              END;@B@@@@            IK
)@@G@@ ELSE " ALL OTHER CHARACTERS  @^@@@@              BEGIN     @D@@@@      IL
)@@G@@          SPACE\TAB; " OUTPUT LEADING SPACES    @C@@@@                PAIM
)@@G@@CK\CHARACTER(LINE\BUFFER(I)); @F@@@@                HORIZONTAL := HORIZOIN
)@@G@@NTAL + LINE\CHAR\WIDTH(I);    @#@@@@              END;@#@@@@           EIO
)@@G@@ND;   @B@@@@END; " OF PROCEDURE PACK\SPINTRONIC\LINE  @[@@@@"     @B@@@@IP
)@@G@@" PROCEDURE TO HANDLE TRANSPARENT OUTPUT  @[@@@@"     @F@@@@PROCEDURE SPIQ
)@@G@@INTRONIC\TRANSPARENT\OUTPUT EXPORTED ('SPINTNSDAT')   @[@@@@BEGIN @[@@@@IR
)@@G@@      @ @@@@DECLARE   CHAR: WORD INTEGER; @[@@@@      @B@@@@          WHIS
)@@G@@ILE TRANSPARENT\OUTPUT DO     @#@@@@           BEGIN  @C@@@@            IT
)@@G@@ CHAR := GET\TRANSPARENT\CHARACTER; @D@@@@             IF TRANSPARENT\OUIU
)@@G@@TPUT THEN " STUFF IT    @D@@@@                PACK\CHARACTER(CHAR); " SEIV
)@@G@@ND IT OFF   @ @@@@           END; " WHILE LOOP  @B@@@@END; " OF PROCEDURIW
)@@G@@E TRANSPARENT OUTPUT    @[@@@@"     @F@@@@" ROUTINE TO SPACEOUT SPACE\OUIX
)@@G@@T BLANKS  SPACE\OUT IS IN INTERNAL  @]@@@@" UNITS.    @[@@@@"     @^@@@@IY
)@@G@@PROCEDURE SPACE\TAB     @[@@@@BEGIN @A@@@@          IF SPACE\OUT NE 0 THIZ
)@@G@@EN    @#@@@@           BEGIN  @#@@@@SEND\SPEED\TAB:   @E@@@@            JA
)@@G@@ IF SPEED\TAB\POS EQ (HORIZONTAL+SPACE\OUT) THEN@D@@@@              BEGIJB
)@@G@@N " EXECUTE CURRENTLY SET SPEED TAB @B@@@@"               PACK\CHARACTERJC
)@@G@@(O'177');   @B@@@@                PACK\CHARACTER(ESCAPE);   @B@@@@      JD
)@@G@@          PACK\CHARACTER(SPEED\TAB);@#@@@@              END;@E@@@@      JE
)@@G@@       ELSE IF SPACE\OUT//SPACEBAND\WIDTH GT 7 THEN   @G@@@@            JF
)@@G@@  BEGIN " SET AND EXECUTE SPEED TAB RATHER THAN SPACE OUT   @E@@@@      JG
)@@G@@          SPEED\TAB\POS := HORIZONTAL + SPACE\OUT;    @F@@@@            JH
)@@G@@    TAB\COLUMN := SPEED\TAB\POS // SPACEBAND\WIDTH;   @B@@@@"           JI
)@@G@@    PACK\CHARACTER(O'177');   @B@@@@                PACK\CHARACTER(ESCAPJJ
)@@G@@E);   @C@@@@                PACK\CHARACTER(SET\SPEED\TAB);  @D@@@@      JK
)@@G@@          PACK\CHARACTER(TAB\COLUMN//100+O'60');@F@@@@                PAJL
)@@G@@CK\CHARACTER(MOD(TAB\COLUMN,100)//10+O'60');    @E@@@@                PAJM
)@@G@@CK\CHARACTER(MOD(TAB\COLUMN,10)+O'60');   @A@@@@                GOTO SENJN
)@@G@@D\SPEED\TAB;@#@@@@              END;@C@@@@             ELSE " BETTER TO JO
)@@G@@JUST SPACE OUT    @^@@@@              BEGIN     @E@@@@                FOJP
)@@G@@R K := 1 TO SPACE\OUT//SPACEBAND\WIDTH DO @E@@@@                   PACK\JQ
)@@G@@CHARACTER(BLANK); " PACK BLANKS     @C@@@@              END; " PACK BLANJR
)@@G@@KS TO SPACE OUT   @H@@@@             HORIZONTAL := HORIZONTAL + SPACE\OUJS
)@@G@@T; " UPDATE CURRENT POSITION  @C@@@@             SPACE\OUT := 0; " SPACEJT
)@@G@@ OUT DONE   @#@@@@           END;   @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @D@@@@" CLOSJU
)@@G@@E THE LINE AND OUTPUT IT TO THE FINAL MEDIUM    @[@@@@"     @E@@@@" DUMPJV
)@@G@@ THE LINE OUT  BUT FIRST BLANK FILL THE LAST WORD     @[@@@@"     @E@@@@JW
)@@G@@PROCEDURE OUTPUT\SPINTRONIC\LINE EXPORTED ('SPINENDLIN')    @[@@@@BEGIN JX
)@@G@@@A@@@@          OUTPUT\LINE; " DUMP LINE  @E@@@@          HORIZONTAL := JY
)@@G@@0; " SET TO BEGINNING OF OUTPUT LINE@C@@@@          SPACE\OUT := 0; " NOJZ
)@@G@@ SPACING EITHER   @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @C@@@@" UNUSED ENTRY POINTS FOKA
)@@G@@R SPINTRONIC HANDLER.   @[@@@@"     @H@@@@PROCEDURE SPINTRONIC\START\OF\KB
)@@G@@TAKE        EXPORTED ('SPINSTRTAK') BEGIN END;  @H@@@@PROCEDURE SPINTRONKC
)@@G@@IC\END\OF\TAKE          EXPORTED ('SPINENDTAK') BEGIN END;  @H@@@@PROCEDKD
)@@G@@URE SPINTRONIC\INTERNAL\FONT\CHANGE EXPORTED ('SPININFONT') BEGIN END;  KE
)@@G@@@H@@@@PROCEDURE SPINTRONIC\EXTERNAL\FONT\CHANGE EXPORTED ('SPINEXFONT') KF
)@@G@@BEGIN END;  @H@@@@PROCEDURE SPINTRONIC\EXTERNAL\WIDTH       EXPORTED ('SKG
)@@G@@PINEXWIDT') BEGIN END;  @H@@@@PROCEDURE SPINTRONIC\SUPERIOR\BEGIN       KH
)@@G@@EXPORTED ('SPINDSIB')   BEGIN END;  @H@@@@PROCEDURE SPINTRONIC\SUPERIOR\KI
)@@G@@SWITCH      EXPORTED ('SPINDSIS')   BEGIN END;  @H@@@@PROCEDURE SPINTRONKJ
)@@G@@IC\SUPERIOR\END         EXPORTED ('SPINDSIE')   BEGIN END;  @H@@@@PROCEDKK
)@@G@@URE SPINTRONIC\ESCAPE\FOR\HANDLER   EXPORTED ('SPINESCAPE') BEGIN END;  KL
)@@G@@@[@@@@"     @[@@@@TERM; ___@@@RE(1) := 0; @E@@@@*[S@@@*SDFF*@[@@@@MODULEKM
)@@G@@@A@@@@          COPY ('DEFINES',IMPORTED);@B@@@@          COPY ('CARD-DEKN
)@@G@@F',IMPORTED);     @B@@@@          COPY ('CHAR-SIZE',IMPORTED);    @B@@@@KO
)@@G@@          COPY ('AREA-DEF',IMPORTED);     @B@@@@          COPY ('SCAN-PRKP
)@@G@@OCS',IMPORTED);   @B@@@@          COPY ('STAGING-DEF',IMPORTED);  @B@@@@KQ
)@@G@@          COPY ('SYMBOL-DEF',IMPORTED);   @B@@@@          COPY ('TITLE-DKR
)@@G@@EF',IMPORTED);    @B@@@@          COPY ('UNIT-COMMON',IMPORTED);  @B@@@@KS
)@@G@@          COPY ('WARNING-DEF',IMPORTED);  @[@@@@      @F@@@@PROCEDURE PAKT
)@@G@@CK\CHARACTER(CHAR: WORD INTEGER) IMPORTED ('PAKCHR'); @[@@@@      @F@@@@KU
)@@G@@PROCEDURE GET\TRANSPARENT\CHARACTER IMPORTED ('GETTRANSCHAR')     @A@@@@KV
)@@G@@             RESULT WORD INTEGER;   @[@@@@      @B@@@@PROCEDURE OUTPUT\LKW
)@@G@@INE IMPORTED ('OPL');   @[@@@@      @E@@@@PROCEDURE SET\ALL\AREA\LINE\WIKX
)@@G@@DTHS IMPORTED ('SETALLINWID');@[@@@@      @G@@@@DECLARE   LEADING\FOR\DEKY
)@@G@@VICE: WORD INTEGER STATIC IMPORTED ('LEDDEV');  @[@@@@      @C@@@@DECLARKZ
)@@G@@E   SKIP: WORD INTEGER STATIC IMPORTED;   @[@@@@      @[@@@@"     @#@@@@LA
)@@G@@" LOCAL STORAGE   @[@@@@"     @H@@@@DECLARE   XXXX: WORD INTEGER; " GETSLB
)@@G@@ RID OF COLLECTOR ERRORS WHEN NO DBANK    @[@@@@"     @D@@@@PROCEDURE INLC
)@@G@@ITIALIZE\QUALTERM EXPORTED ('QUALTINIT')  @[@@@@BEGIN @A@@@@          UNLD
)@@G@@IT\DEVICE\WIDTH := 1; " @E@@@@          NEW\CHAR\WIDTH := 10; " TEN CHARLE
)@@G@@ACTERS PER INCH   @B@@@@          CHANGE\CHARS\PER\INCH; " SET IT @[@@@@LF
)@@G@@"     @^@@@@" SET STANDARD MARGINS  @[@@@@"     @B@@@@          TOP\MARGLG
)@@G@@IN := INCH\DISTANCE;    @B@@@@          BOTTOM\MARGIN := INCH\DISTANCE; LH
)@@G@@@C@@@@          PAGE\HEIGHT := INCH\DISTANCE * 11;    @C@@@@          PALI
)@@G@@GE\WIDTH := INCH\DISTANCE * 8.5;    @B@@@@          LEFT\MARGIN := INCH\LJ
)@@G@@DISTANCE;   @B@@@@          RIGHT\MARGIN := INCH\DISTANCE;  @A@@@@      LK
)@@G@@    SET\ALL\AREA\LINE\WIDTHS; @F@@@@          NEW\CHAR\HEIGHT := 6; " SELL
)@@G@@T 6 LINES PER INCH STANDARD   @B@@@@          CHANGE\LINES\PER\INCH; " SLM
)@@G@@ET IT @F@@@@          PAGE\OFFSET := 0; " VIRTUAL AND PHYSICAL PAGE THE LN
)@@G@@SAME  @E@@@@          DEVICE\BACKSPACES := TRUE; " WE CAN BACKSPACE     LO
)@@G@@@F@@@@          DEVICE\LETTER\SPACES := FALSE; " CANNOT LETTERSPACE     LP
)@@G@@@D@@@@          DEVICE\JUSTIFIES := FALSE; " WE MUST DO IT  @F@@@@      LQ
)@@G@@    DEVICE\HYPHEN\CHAR := MINUS; " STANDARD HYPHEN CHAR     @C@@@@      LR
)@@G@@    MUTILATE := FALSE; " DO NOT MUTILATE  @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@      @D@@@@LS
)@@G@@PROCEDURE PAGEUP\QUALTERM EXPORTED ('QUALTTOPFRM')    @[@@@@BEGIN @D@@@@LT
)@@G@@          SKIP := 0; " KILL ANY REMAING SKIP COUNT    @E@@@@          PALU
)@@G@@CK\CHARACTER(FORM\FEED); " OUTPUT FORM FEED     @B@@@@          OUTPUT\QLV
)@@G@@UALTERM\LINE; " DUMP IT @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @B@@@@" DO ACTUAL LINE FLW
)@@G@@EEDS FOR THE QUALTERM   @[@@@@"     @D@@@@PROCEDURE LINE\FEED\QUALTERM ELX
)@@G@@XPORTED ('QUALTLEADNG') @[@@@@BEGIN @F@@@@          SKIP := SKIP + LEADILY
)@@G@@NG\FOR\DEVICE // SKIP\DISTANCE;     @[@@@@END;  @[@@@@"     @A@@@@PROCEDLZ
